<font color="#ffff00">But you were right.</font>

14:14.040 --> 14:16.720
<font color="#ffff00">They dare to question your holy</font>
<font color="#ffff00">status.</font>

14:17.800 --> 14:20.720
<font color="#ffff00">Monsieur Dupuis simply said what</font>
<font color="#ffff00">they were all thinking.</font>

14:22.520 --> 14:24.320
<font color="#ffff00">And you know...</font>

14:24.320 --> 14:26.080
<font color="#ffff00">you are chosen by God.</font>

14:30.600 --> 14:32.560
<font color="#ffffff">Perhaps the time has come to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">show them.</font>

14:38.520 --> 14:41.800
<font color="#ffffff">Two years ago, one of my galleons</font>
<font color="#ffffff">set sail for the Americas.</font>

14:41.800 --> 14:43.840
<font color="#ffffff">The vessel appeared robust.</font>

14:43.840 --> 14:45.680
<font color="#ffffff">The captain declared it seaworthy.</font>

14:47.360 --> 14:49.880
<font color="#ffffff">But he had spotted some woodworm.</font>

14:49.880 --> 14:51.840
<font color="#ffffff">Just a little.</font>

14:51.840 --> 14:53.600
<font color="#ffffff">A few tiny larvae,</font>

14:53.600 --> 14:55.600
<font color="#ffffff">presumed to be innocent stowaways.</font>

14:57.480 --> 15:00.000
<font color="#ffffff">The ship crossed the ocean with</font>
<font color="#ffffff">ease.</font>

15:00.000 --> 15:01.960
<font color="#ffffff">But on the return journey,</font>

15:01.960 --> 15:06.360
<font color="#ffffff">the sails were raised and the</font>
<font color="#ffffff">main mast crumbled.</font>

15:06.360 --> 15:07.960
<font color="#ffffff">What was thought to be woodworm</font>

15:07.960 --> 15:10.160
<font color="#ffffff">turned out to be the deathwatch</font>
<font color="#ffffff">beetle,</font>

15:10.160 --> 15:12.480
<font color="#ffffff">and the body of the craft was</font>
<font color="#ffffff">riddled,</font>

15:12.480 --> 15:13.920
<font color="#ffffff">eaten from within.</font>

15:15.840 --> 15:19.960
<font color="#ffffff">You see, the time to deal with the</font>
<font color="#ffffff">menace was before he set sail.</font>

15:22.160 --> 15:24.440
<font color="#ffffff">He could have easily replaced a few</font>
<font color="#ffffff">timbers.</font>

15:27.080 --> 15:29.200
<font color="#ffffff">His mistake was to ignore the</font>
<font color="#ffffff">threat...</font>

15:32.000 --> 15:33.880
<font color="#ffffff">..however small it appeared.</font>

15:35.480 --> 15:37.320
<font color="#ffffff">It became an infestation.</font>

15:42.000 --> 15:45.600
<font color="#ffffff">I want to deal with the Protestant</font>
<font color="#ffffff">problem as a matter of priority,</font>

15:45.600 --> 15:49.240
<font color="#ffffff">starting with a detailed inventory</font>
<font color="#ffffff">of the Protestants under my roof.</font>

15:51.600 --> 15:53.360
<font color="#00ffff">But...</font>

15:53.360 --> 15:56.680
<font color="#00ffff">they have been compliant and loyal.</font>

15:56.680 --> 16:01.160
<font color="#00ffff">Their faith is private, between the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">individual and God...</font>

16:01.160 --> 16:03.120
<font color="#ffff00">They dispute the natural order.</font>

16:03.120 --> 16:05.320
<font color="#ffff00">They challenge the authority of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">priest,</font>

16:05.320 --> 16:08.480
<font color="#ffff00">Pope and His Majesty as our</font>
<font color="#ffff00">God-chosen King.</font>

16:08.480 --> 16:12.120
<font color="#00ff00">Every Huguenot's a threat while he</font>
<font color="#00ff00">shares faith with William of Orange.</font>

16:15.000 --> 16:17.240
<font color="#00ffff">Nevertheless...</font>

16:17.240 --> 16:21.400
<font color="#00ffff">Could I urge His Majesty to remain</font>
<font color="#00ffff">lenient,</font>

16:21.400 --> 16:24.120
<font color="#00ffff">if only for reasons of taxation?</font>

16:24.120 --> 16:26.480
<font color="#00ff00">His Majesty should also remember</font>

16:26.480 --> 16:29.360
<font color="#00ff00">there is legislation in place</font>
<font color="#00ff00">regarding</font>

16:29.360 --> 16:31.640
<font color="#00ff00">the rights of all faiths.</font>

16:31.640 --> 16:33.120
<font color="#ffffff">Why so fearful, gentlemen?</font>

16:34.560 --> 16:36.400
<font color="#ffffff">I am a reasonable man.</font>

16:36.400 --> 16:38.120
<font color="#ffffff">I do not wish to be cruel.</font>

16:38.120 --> 16:42.040
<font color="#ffff00">The challenge is to help them</font>
<font color="#ffff00">realise their mistake and encourage</font>

16:42.040 --> 16:44.400
<font color="#ffff00">them to return to the one true</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Church.</font>

16:44.400 --> 16:46.200
<font color="#ffffff">Precisely. So, I want you to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">identify</font>

16:46.200 --> 16:50.200
<font color="#ffffff">all Protestant businesses</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and let them know that</font>

16:50.200 --> 16:55.320
<font color="#ffffff">the King would look more kindly on</font>
<font color="#ffffff">them if they were to recant.</font>

16:55.320 --> 16:56.440
<font color="#00ffff">And if they don't?</font>

16:59.200 --> 17:01.040
<font color="#ffffff">Their fate is in their own hands.</font>

17:06.400 --> 17:10.160
<font color="#00ffff">Now we must accept a woman as the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">King's principal adviser!</font>

17:10.160 --> 17:12.040
<font color="#00ff00">I see no problem.</font>

17:12.040 --> 17:15.040
<font color="#00ffff">I foresee many, if he continues to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">reject our input.</font>

17:15.040 --> 17:17.280
<font color="#00ff00">Because you may have to work</font>
<font color="#00ff00">harder?</font>

17:17.280 --> 17:19.079
<font color="#00ffff">I strive night and day already.</font>

17:19.079 --> 17:21.119
<font color="#00ffff">I give the King my every waking</font>
<font color="#00ffff">minute!</font>

17:21.119 --> 17:24.079
<font color="#00ff00">I concede that with this new</font>
<font color="#00ff00">arrangement we must be vigilant.</font>

17:24.079 --> 17:26.400
<font color="#00ffff">Vigilant? We should be up in arms!</font>

17:26.400 --> 17:30.160
<font color="#00ffff">The edict of Nantes is there to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">protect such vulnerable minorities.</font>

17:30.160 --> 17:34.800
<font color="#00ffff">If the King tears it up, there's no</font>
<font color="#00ffff">telling where it will end.</font>

17:40.920 --> 17:42.240
<font color="#00ff00">Do you advocate mutiny?</font>

17:44.160 --> 17:47.120
<font color="#00ffff">I ask the council to reject naked</font>
<font color="#00ffff">sectarianism.</font>

17:47.120 --> 17:48.640
<font color="#00ffff">This is religious bigotry.</font>

17:50.200 --> 17:52.080
<font color="#00ff00">The King has his reasons.</font>

17:52.080 --> 17:54.840
<font color="#00ff00">It's our job to facilitate him.</font>

17:54.840 --> 17:56.600
<font color="#00ffff">It is our job to do what is right.</font>

18:01.640 --> 18:03.800
<font color="#00ffff">A moment, Monsieur Bontemps.</font>

18:03.800 --> 18:05.520
<font color="#00ff00">I have business to attend to.</font>

18:05.520 --> 18:07.360
<font color="#00ffff">I thought you should be informed of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a murder.</font>

18:13.920 --> 18:16.360
<font color="#00ffff">You've been acquainted with the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">governor of the Bastille.</font>

18:16.360 --> 18:17.880
<font color="#00ff00">And this concerns me how?</font>

18:19.200 --> 18:22.320
<font color="#00ffff">I wondered if you knew anyone who</font>
<font color="#00ffff">might have reason to wish him dead.</font>

18:23.600 --> 18:25.680
<font color="#00ff00">In his line of work, I suspect there</font>
<font color="#00ff00">are many.</font>

18:25.680 --> 18:27.600
<font color="#00ff00">And if you don't mind my</font>
<font color="#00ff00">reminding you,</font>

18:27.600 --> 18:30.880
<font color="#00ff00">your principal priority should be</font>
<font color="#00ff00">protecting the Royal Family.</font>

18:30.880 --> 18:32.120
<font color="#00ffff">It always has been.</font>

18:33.320 --> 18:35.240
<font color="#00ff00">The Queen has fallen ill.</font>

18:35.240 --> 18:37.720
<font color="#00ff00">Have you ruled out the possibility</font>
<font color="#00ff00">of a poisoner?</font>

18:39.000 --> 18:41.360
<font color="#00ff00">Good day, Monsieur Marchal.</font>

18:44.840 --> 18:46.120
<font color="#ffff00">The death of the devil.</font>

18:47.480 --> 18:50.040
<font color="#ffff00">I read about this in my studies.</font>

18:50.040 --> 18:51.960
<font color="#00ffff">So, it's in the Bible?</font>

18:51.960 --> 18:54.400
<font color="#ffff00">It is suggested, yes.</font>

18:54.400 --> 18:56.360
<font color="#ffff00">The actual story's in the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Apocrypha.</font>

18:57.360 --> 19:02.440
<font color="#ffff00">A collection of holy scriptures that</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the Church deems troublesome.</font>

19:04.000 --> 19:05.880
<font color="#ffff00">The insignia.</font>

19:07.400 --> 19:09.240
<font color="#00ffff">You've seen that before?</font>

19:09.240 --> 19:10.880
<font color="#ffff00">In Vatican records.</font>

19:10.880 --> 19:13.280
<font color="#ffff00">The symbol of an ancient sect,</font>

19:13.280 --> 19:17.240
<font color="#ffff00">the Knights of Damascus from the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">third Crusade, I believe.</font>

19:17.240 --> 19:20.920
<font color="#ffff00">They were a clandestine order said</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to have just one aim -</font>

19:20.920 --> 19:22.920
<font color="#ffff00">to protect the Catholic Church</font>

19:22.920 --> 19:25.840
<font color="#ffff00">and dispose of its enemies</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with impunity.</font>

20:17.560 --> 20:19.760
<font color="#00ffff">What do you pray for,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Monsieur Bontemps?</font>

20:25.680 --> 20:27.480
<font color="#00ff00">Deliverance from evil.</font>

20:30.360 --> 20:32.200
<font color="#00ffff">I wish to see the prisoner.</font>

20:35.400 --> 20:37.440
<font color="#00ff00">I will not speak of that here.</font>

20:38.600 --> 20:40.480
<font color="#00ffff">You need not speak at all.</font>

20:40.480 --> 20:42.880
<font color="#00ffff">Just listen. </font><font color="#00ff00">No, you listen to me.</font>

20:45.160 --> 20:47.320
<font color="#00ff00">I've run this palace.</font>

20:47.320 --> 20:50.320
<font color="#00ff00">My services are exclusively to the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">King.</font>

20:51.680 --> 20:57.240
<font color="#00ffff">There is a higher authority to which</font>
<font color="#00ffff">we both must answer,</font>

20:57.240 --> 21:01.040
<font color="#00ffff">and you will take me to the prisoner</font>
<font color="#00ffff">at your earliest convenience.</font>

21:11.840 --> 21:16.120
<font color="#ffffff">We gather to remember our good</font>
<font color="#ffffff">friend, Olivier...</font>

21:17.760 --> 21:19.400
<font color="#ffffff">..taken from us so cruelly.</font>

21:21.760 --> 21:24.480
<font color="#ffffff">We ask you, our Lord,</font>

21:24.480 --> 21:25.720
<font color="#ffffff">to keep him safe.</font>

21:27.280 --> 21:30.000
<font color="#ffffff">And to fold his family in the palm</font>
<font color="#ffffff">of your hand.</font>

21:30.000 --> 21:31.520
<font color="#ffffff">Amen.</font>

21:31.520 --> 21:32.960
<font color="#ffffff">ALL: </font><font color="#ffff00">Amen.</font>

21:36.760 --> 21:38.160
<font color="#00ffff">I'm so sorry.</font>

21:44.400 --> 21:46.520
<font color="#00ff00">It's from the palace.</font>

21:46.520 --> 21:48.320
<font color="#00ff00">A warning of what's to come.</font>

21:53.640 --> 21:56.400
<font color="#ffffff">It's not enough to tax us to the</font>
<font color="#ffffff">hilt and murder our friends.</font>

21:56.400 --> 21:58.280
<font color="#ffffff">Now he wants us to give up our</font>
<font color="#ffffff">religion!</font>

21:58.280 --> 22:01.120
<font color="#00ff00">It's an empty threat. </font><font color="#ffffff">We've seen</font>
<font color="#ffffff">what he's capable of.</font>

22:01.120 --> 22:03.440
<font color="#ffffff">We have to stand up to him.</font>

22:03.440 --> 22:07.360
<font color="#ffffff">So, what are you going to do?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Recant just to please the King?</font>

22:07.360 --> 22:09.680
<font color="#00ff00">Get back to work.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">While we still have it!</font>

22:22.560 --> 22:24.440
<font color="#00ffff">I will interview the prisoner alone.</font>

22:26.680 --> 22:28.720
<font color="#00ff00">Why is he tethered?</font>

22:28.720 --> 22:31.960
<font color="#00ffff">For his own safety.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">You may remain outside.</font>

22:35.600 --> 22:37.760
<font color="#00ff00">I've protected this man all my life.</font>

22:38.760 --> 22:42.440
<font color="#00ff00">I will not see him suffer now!</font>

22:42.440 --> 22:44.680
<font color="#ffff00">The King will end my torture soon.</font>

22:44.680 --> 22:46.360
<font color="#00ff00">The King knows nothing of this.</font>

22:46.360 --> 22:48.200
<font color="#00ff00">And thus it will remain.</font>

22:57.360 --> 22:58.960
<font color="#ffffff">An uninvited guest.</font>

22:58.960 --> 23:00.920
<font color="#00ffff">I've worked out what you're doing.</font>

23:00.920 --> 23:03.320
<font color="#ffffff">And you wish to join me at my table.</font>

23:03.320 --> 23:06.640
<font color="#00ffff">You invited the Roman cleric to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Versailles, didn't you?</font>

23:06.640 --> 23:08.360
<font color="#ffffff">Why on earth would I do that?</font>

23:08.360 --> 23:11.120
<font color="#00ffff">Because I think you might be a lot</font>
<font color="#00ffff">closer to the Vatican</font>

23:11.120 --> 23:12.400
<font color="#00ffff">than you're letting on.</font>

23:12.400 --> 23:15.280
<font color="#ffffff">Is this more paranoia from your</font>
<font color="#ffffff">fevered imagination?</font>

23:15.280 --> 23:17.160
<font color="#00ffff">Give me a straight answer.</font>

23:17.160 --> 23:20.720
<font color="#ffffff">I appointed you to counsel for your</font>
<font color="#ffffff">new-found maturity.</font>

23:20.720 --> 23:23.080
<font color="#ffffff">Don't give me more cause to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">regret it.</font>

23:23.080 --> 23:26.560
<font color="#00ffff">Why is the Vatican holding the man</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in the iron mask?</font>

23:26.560 --> 23:29.080
<font color="#ffffff">My dear Philippe,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">since that bang on the head,</font>

23:29.080 --> 23:32.520
<font color="#ffffff">your behaviour has been erratic,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">at times alarming.</font>

23:32.520 --> 23:34.880
<font color="#ffffff">This madness must stop.</font>

23:34.880 --> 23:37.880
<font color="#ffffff">I need you by my side, not chasing</font>
<font color="#ffffff">lost causes.</font>

23:39.160 --> 23:40.760
<font color="#ffffff">I'm losing you, brother.</font>

23:43.000 --> 23:45.560
<font color="#00ffff">I fear it is I who is losing you...</font>

23:45.560 --> 23:46.920
<font color="#00ffff">brother.</font>

23:53.040 --> 23:55.400
<font color="#ffffff">Are we really expected to do</font>
<font color="#ffffff">nothing?</font>

23:57.320 --> 24:00.480
<font color="#ffff00">Accept the world we live in.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Paint on a sunny visage.</font>

24:00.480 --> 24:02.640
<font color="#ffff00">There's nothing else one can do.</font>

24:02.640 --> 24:05.040
<font color="#ffffff">I dislike my name being on a list.</font>

24:05.040 --> 24:06.840
<font color="#ffffff">But it's my nephew that concerns me.</font>

24:06.840 --> 24:09.480
<font color="#ffffff">His entire future could be in</font>
<font color="#ffffff">jeopardy</font>

24:09.480 --> 24:11.480
<font color="#ffffff">with a stroke of a catholic pen,</font>

24:11.480 --> 24:14.200
<font color="#ffffff">along with all other decent</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Protestant businessmen.</font>

24:15.800 --> 24:19.280
<font color="#ffff00">And, on that subject, I had been</font>
<font color="#ffff00">considering recanting myself,</font>

24:19.280 --> 24:21.040
<font color="#ffff00">so we might have more in common.</font>

24:23.000 --> 24:24.560
<font color="#ffffff">You would become a Protestant?</font>

24:25.920 --> 24:26.960
<font color="#ffff00">Well...</font>

24:28.640 --> 24:30.360
<font color="#ffff00">Not the way things are now,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">obviously.</font>

24:32.440 --> 24:35.680
<font color="#ffff00">But, clearly, the sensible thing to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">do now is</font>

24:35.680 --> 24:37.920
<font color="#ffff00">for you to become a Catholic.</font>

24:37.920 --> 24:39.680
<font color="#ffffff">You don't know me at all, do you?</font>

24:41.240 --> 24:43.640
<font color="#ffff00">I know you most intimately.</font>

24:45.280 --> 24:48.120
<font color="#ffffff">We had sex. Don't imagine that gives</font>
<font color="#ffffff">you access to my heart.</font>

24:50.080 --> 24:51.240
<font color="#ffff00">But if...</font>

24:52.480 --> 24:54.560
<font color="#ffff00">..we were to marry as Catholics,</font>

24:54.560 --> 24:57.360
<font color="#ffff00">that would secure your position in</font>
<font color="#ffff00">court.</font>

24:58.840 --> 25:00.320
<font color="#ffffff">I need no man.</font>

25:00.320 --> 25:03.880
<font color="#ffffff">And I wouldn't marry you if you were</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the last specimen on this earth.</font>

25:07.680 --> 25:12.080
<font color="#ffffff">Ah! The famous shoemaker,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">alone in the palace.</font>

25:12.080 --> 25:14.280
<font color="#ffffff">Have you lost your way?</font>

25:14.280 --> 25:16.160
<font color="#ffff00">No. Actually, I...</font>

25:17.240 --> 25:19.320
<font color="#ffff00">I was hoping to talk</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to the Duc d'Orleans.</font>

25:19.320 --> 25:21.920
<font color="#ffffff">Perhaps I can help? </font><font color="#ffff00">Well...</font>

25:23.600 --> 25:26.400
<font color="#ffff00">I'm a loyal Frenchman, sir.</font>

25:26.400 --> 25:27.880
<font color="#ffff00">I serve the palace as best I can.</font>

25:29.920 --> 25:32.200
<font color="#ffff00">But I'm afraid that</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I may lose business...</font>

25:33.680 --> 25:35.080
<font color="#ffff00">..because I'm a Protestant.</font>

25:36.560 --> 25:39.360
<font color="#ffffff">You're in luck, my boy. </font><font color="#ffff00">Really?</font>

25:39.360 --> 25:42.400
<font color="#ffffff">I wish to commission boots</font>
<font color="#ffffff">for my entire infantry.</font>

25:44.240 --> 25:46.360
<font color="#ffff00">Yes, sir, I'd be delighted, sir.</font>

25:46.360 --> 25:49.600
<font color="#ffffff">The contract is yours in perpetuity.</font>

25:49.600 --> 25:51.760
<font color="#ffffff">On condition...</font>

25:51.760 --> 25:53.120
<font color="#ffffff">that you'll recant.</font>

26:08.080 --> 26:10.560
<font color="#ffffff">Did you talk to the Duc d'Orleans?</font>

26:10.560 --> 26:13.360
<font color="#ffff00">There's no point.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">This can only end one way.</font>

26:14.840 --> 26:16.640
<font color="#ffffff">Well, so be it.</font>

26:16.640 --> 26:20.400
<font color="#ffffff">We can cope. </font><font color="#ffff00">We've been offered</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a contract for the military.</font>

26:22.160 --> 26:24.040
<font color="#ffff00">It would secure</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the business for decades.</font>

26:28.000 --> 26:29.320
<font color="#ffffff">But?</font>

26:37.440 --> 26:40.920
<font color="#ffffff">Guillaume, you'd recant your faith?</font>

26:40.920 --> 26:43.080
<font color="#ffff00">Just hear me out.</font>

26:43.080 --> 26:46.360
<font color="#ffffff">I don't believe it.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">It's just saying a few words!</font>

26:46.360 --> 26:49.000
<font color="#ffffff">A few words before God.</font>

26:49.000 --> 26:52.200
<font color="#ffff00">It's about being practical</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in the face of adversity.</font>

26:52.200 --> 26:54.440
<font color="#ffffff">You'd be rejecting everything</font>
<font color="#ffffff">our father stood for.</font>

26:54.440 --> 26:57.360
<font color="#ffff00">Our father was a businessman, he</font>
<font color="#ffff00">understood how these things work.</font>

26:57.360 --> 26:58.720
<font color="#ffffff">Yeah!</font>

26:58.720 --> 27:02.040
<font color="#ffffff">And he knew that principles</font>
<font color="#ffffff">were more important than money.</font>

27:02.040 --> 27:04.800
<font color="#ffff00">I wouldn't be doing it for me!</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I'm thinking of the lads!</font>

27:04.800 --> 27:06.920
<font color="#ffff00">They've been loyal through</font>
<font color="#ffff00">all the bad times.</font>

27:06.920 --> 27:09.560
<font color="#ffff00">This is a chance to save their jobs!</font>
<font color="#ffff00">They'd be grateful!</font>

27:11.360 --> 27:12.880
<font color="#ffffff">You don't care about them.</font>

27:15.200 --> 27:16.360
<font color="#ffffff">This is about you.</font>

27:17.840 --> 27:19.600
<font color="#ffffff">You want to be rich.</font>

27:19.600 --> 27:21.880
<font color="#ffffff">Just so long as you can</font>
<font color="#ffffff">be a part of Versailles!</font>

27:29.840 --> 27:32.280
<font color="#ffffff">Well, I won't give in</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to the King's blackmail.</font>

27:32.280 --> 27:34.880
<font color="#ffffff">If you've got any heart left,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">then neither will you.</font>

27:53.320 --> 27:57.480
<font color="#ffffff">So, what earth-shattering challenge</font>
<font color="#ffffff">are we wrestling with today?</font>

27:57.480 --> 27:59.960
<font color="#ffff00">Matters of the heart.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">You wouldn't understand.</font>

28:04.680 --> 28:07.040
<font color="#00ffff">The Chevalier de Lorraine</font>
<font color="#00ffff">has fallen in love.</font>

28:08.200 --> 28:12.040
<font color="#ffffff">He's purloined a new mirror?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">No. The Duchesse d'Angers.</font>

28:14.480 --> 28:16.880
<font color="#ffffff">Him? With a woman?</font>

28:18.240 --> 28:21.200
<font color="#ffff00">They lack stamina but they offer</font>
<font color="#ffff00">one or two more options than men.</font>

28:21.200 --> 28:23.080
<font color="#ffffff">DOOR OPENS</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I am here, you know.</font>

28:25.320 --> 28:27.720
<font color="#00ff00">The Queen requests</font>
<font color="#00ff00">your presence, madam.</font>

28:33.920 --> 28:36.120
<font color="#00ffff">Don't discuss any juicy</font>
<font color="#00ffff">matters without me.</font>

28:52.240 --> 28:53.880
<font color="#ffff00">You have somewhere to be?</font>

28:54.880 --> 28:55.920
<font color="#ffffff">Somewhere else.</font>

28:57.560 --> 28:59.520
<font color="#ffff00">I'm not trying to seduce you.</font>

29:01.080 --> 29:05.120
<font color="#ffff00">I just...hoped we could still talk</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to each other without rancour.</font>

29:15.600 --> 29:16.680
<font color="#ffff00">So?</font>

29:19.680 --> 29:20.720
<font color="#ffff00">How've you been?</font>

29:22.080 --> 29:23.520
<font color="#ffffff">Busy.</font>

29:23.520 --> 29:25.120
<font color="#ffffff">You?</font>

29:25.120 --> 29:26.160
<font color="#ffff00">After a fashion.</font>

29:29.400 --> 29:30.440
<font color="#ffff00">How's your love life?</font>

29:32.960 --> 29:34.000
<font color="#ffffff">Solitary.</font>

29:36.280 --> 29:39.680
<font color="#ffff00">The true love that never</font>
<font color="#ffff00">lets a man down.</font>

29:39.680 --> 29:41.640
<font color="#ffffff">You are really in love</font>
<font color="#ffffff">with that woman?</font>

29:45.920 --> 29:47.480
<font color="#ffff00">I don't know.</font>

29:47.480 --> 29:50.080
<font color="#ffffff">Can't remember what it feels like.</font>

29:50.080 --> 29:52.400
<font color="#ffff00">It makes me feel marvellous,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">thank you.</font>

29:52.400 --> 29:54.120
<font color="#ffffff">I remember it was good.</font>

29:55.120 --> 29:56.760
<font color="#ffffff">I know that much.</font>

29:56.760 --> 29:59.360
<font color="#ffff00">Having a real reason</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to get out of bed in the morning.</font>

30:01.000 --> 30:02.040
<font color="#ffffff">Or staying in.</font>

30:09.000 --> 30:10.160
<font color="#ffffff">So what's the problem?</font>

30:11.920 --> 30:14.320
<font color="#ffff00">She's proving quite a challenge.</font>

30:14.320 --> 30:17.000
<font color="#ffff00">I don't know what to say</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to convince her.</font>

30:20.760 --> 30:22.120
<font color="#ffffff">Don't say anything.</font>

30:25.840 --> 30:27.520
<font color="#ffffff">Find a way to show her.</font>

30:29.560 --> 30:31.600
<font color="#ffffff">SHE HUMS</font>

30:36.520 --> 30:39.400
<font color="#ffffff">DOOR OPENS, CLOSES</font>

30:46.440 --> 30:48.440
<font color="#ffffff">How delightful to see you, my dear.</font>

30:54.520 --> 30:56.320
<font color="#ffffff">I feel fabulous.</font>

30:57.440 --> 30:59.280
<font color="#ffffff">Like a new woman.</font>

30:59.280 --> 31:01.200
<font color="#ffff00">You wished to see me, Your Majesty?</font>

31:02.600 --> 31:04.560
<font color="#ffffff">Yes, I have the appetite of an army.</font>

31:04.560 --> 31:06.320
<font color="#ffffff">Won't you join me in a feast?</font>

31:06.320 --> 31:07.360
<font color="#ffff00">I'd be delighted.</font>

31:08.560 --> 31:10.040
<font color="#ffffff">I can't help but feel I've been</font>

31:10.040 --> 31:12.240
<font color="#ffffff">missing out on the</font>
<font color="#ffffff">pleasures of Versailles.</font>

31:12.240 --> 31:14.640
<font color="#ffffff">Today, I shall drink wine.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Lots and lots of wine.</font>

31:14.640 --> 31:15.920
<font color="#ffff00">If Her Majesty so wishes.</font>

31:19.480 --> 31:20.800
<font color="#ffffff">Mm!</font>

31:23.040 --> 31:28.040
<font color="#ffffff">But first, Her Majesty wants</font>
<font color="#ffffff">a bath of scented rose petals.</font>

31:28.040 --> 31:31.800
<font color="#ffff00">My dear, what on Earth</font>
<font color="#ffff00">are you doing?</font>

31:31.800 --> 31:33.800
<font color="#ffffff">Having some fun.</font>

31:33.800 --> 31:36.520
<font color="#ffffff">A facet of life I have</font>
<font color="#ffffff">resisted for too long.</font>

31:36.520 --> 31:38.800
<font color="#ffffff">Want to take me for a ride</font>
<font color="#ffffff">in the forest?</font>

31:39.880 --> 31:42.360
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps the doctor</font>
<font color="#ffff00">should have a say in that.</font>

31:42.360 --> 31:43.920
<font color="#ffffff">Won't you take me for a ride?</font>

31:46.080 --> 31:48.040
<font color="#ffffff">Touch me again and</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I'll tell Mother.</font>

31:51.480 --> 31:52.520
<font color="#ffffff">She's calling me.</font>

31:55.280 --> 31:56.720
<font color="#ffffff">Can't you hear her?</font>

31:56.720 --> 31:58.760
<font color="#ffffff">FAINT ECHOING VOICES</font>

32:03.160 --> 32:04.520
<font color="#ffffff">I'm coming to you.</font>

32:06.320 --> 32:08.520
<font color="#ffffff">I will embrace you,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">my heavenly angel.</font>

32:10.080 --> 32:13.000
<font color="#00ffff">You need some rest.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">UNHAND ME, YOU FUCKING DOG!</font>

32:13.000 --> 32:14.440
<font color="#ffffff">I'M NOT YOUR PRISONER!</font>

32:16.120 --> 32:17.640
<font color="#ffffff">I can hear you whispering.</font>

32:17.640 --> 32:20.160
<font color="#ffffff">I can see you sneering,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I know what you're doing.</font>

32:20.160 --> 32:22.280
<font color="#ffffff">Tying me up,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">pushing the life from me.</font>

32:36.600 --> 32:37.920
<font color="#ffffff">What's happening to me?</font>

32:40.360 --> 32:41.560
<font color="#ffffff">What's happening to me?</font>

32:47.160 --> 32:48.360
<font color="#ffffff">What's happening to me?</font>

32:49.840 --> 32:51.280
<font color="#ffffff">What's happening to me?</font>

32:53.040 --> 32:56.000
<font color="#ffffff">What's happening to me?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">What's happening to me?</font>

33:02.120 --> 33:03.800
<font color="#ffffff">She's possessed by a demon.</font>

33:03.800 --> 33:05.200
<font color="#ffffff">SHE SHRIEKS</font>

33:07.480 --> 33:08.520
<font color="#ffffff">SHE GASPS</font>

33:11.120 --> 33:12.160
<font color="#ffffff">SHE GASPS</font>

33:23.600 --> 33:25.640
<font color="#ffffff">I have inspected the Queen.</font>

33:27.200 --> 33:30.920
<font color="#ffffff">I believe she is indeed possessed...</font>

33:30.920 --> 33:32.280
<font color="#ffffff">..of a sinister spirit.</font>

33:33.520 --> 33:37.760
<font color="#ffff00">She's sick. It is her own spirit</font>
<font color="#ffff00">that ails her.</font>

33:37.760 --> 33:39.480
<font color="#00ffff">And there is no question of poison?</font>

33:41.240 --> 33:42.840
<font color="#00ff00">The doctor has dismissed it.</font>

33:44.240 --> 33:46.360
<font color="#ffff00">You must go to her side,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">she is heartsore.</font>

33:46.360 --> 33:48.560
<font color="#ffffff">I must advise against that.</font>

33:49.960 --> 33:54.080
<font color="#ffffff">Such spirits can only be</font>
<font color="#ffffff">treated with exorcism.</font>

33:55.480 --> 33:57.880
<font color="#ffffff">Only the power of God...</font>

33:57.880 --> 33:59.840
<font color="#ffffff">can cast it out and save her soul.</font>

34:01.640 --> 34:04.200
<font color="#ffffff">It can be traumatic</font>
<font color="#ffffff">for the unfortunate victim.</font>

34:05.520 --> 34:07.520
<font color="#ffffff">But it is the only option.</font>

34:28.280 --> 34:31.199
<font color="#ffffff">Do you know who saw the Queen</font>
<font color="#ffffff">on the day before she fell ill?</font>

34:35.000 --> 34:38.400
<font color="#ffffff">I want the name of any servant</font>
<font color="#ffffff">who was with her this past week.</font>

34:46.560 --> 34:49.520
<font color="#ffffff">We are in the dark, Louvois.</font>

34:49.520 --> 34:51.239
<font color="#ffffff">Can it be true?</font>

34:51.239 --> 34:53.800
<font color="#ffffff">Our Queen is possessed</font>
<font color="#ffffff">by an evil demon?</font>

34:53.800 --> 34:57.920
<font color="#ffff00">You know as well as I there is not</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a more godly person in the palace.</font>

35:10.040 --> 35:11.200
<font color="#ffffff">Why are you so anxious?</font>

35:13.360 --> 35:14.400
<font color="#ffff00">We are all anxious.</font>

35:31.760 --> 35:34.240
<font color="#ffffff">You startled me.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps that was my intention.</font>

35:37.000 --> 35:38.880
<font color="#ffffff">When did you last see the Queen?</font>

35:38.880 --> 35:42.920
<font color="#ffff00">I've just come from her.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Poor soul is suffering terribly.</font>

35:42.920 --> 35:44.600
<font color="#ffffff">Before she fell ill?</font>

35:44.600 --> 35:45.720
<font color="#ffff00">I met her in the salon.</font>

35:47.280 --> 35:48.640
<font color="#ffff00">Why?</font>

35:48.640 --> 35:52.760
<font color="#ffffff">Her lady-in-waiting claims you were</font>
<font color="#ffffff">in her quarters the previous night.</font>

35:52.760 --> 35:54.400
<font color="#ffff00">Yes, yes.</font>

35:54.400 --> 35:56.480
<font color="#ffff00">Of course, that slipped my mind.</font>

35:56.480 --> 35:58.280
<font color="#ffffff">What were you doing there?</font>

35:58.280 --> 36:00.160
<font color="#00ffff">She was looking for me.</font>

36:00.160 --> 36:02.560
<font color="#00ffff">I get lost in this place</font>
<font color="#00ffff">all the time.</font>

36:02.560 --> 36:04.360
<font color="#ffffff">The Duchesse came to my aid.</font>

36:04.360 --> 36:10.000
<font color="#ffff00">Yes. I showed the Princess to her</font>
<font color="#ffff00">rooms, then retired to bed...alone.</font>

36:11.280 --> 36:14.280
<font color="#ffffff">Such vexation does not</font>
<font color="#ffffff">suit you, Duchesse.</font>

36:29.080 --> 36:30.560
<font color="#00ffff">Well, aren't you going to tell me?</font>

36:31.800 --> 36:33.480
<font color="#ffff00">I don't know what</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you're talking about.</font>

36:33.480 --> 36:35.360
<font color="#00ffff">What were you doing near</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the Queen's rooms?</font>

36:37.360 --> 36:39.360
<font color="#ffff00">I wanted a word with her,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">that's all.</font>

36:39.360 --> 36:42.360
<font color="#00ffff">So why did you let me lie for you?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">It seemed convenient.</font>

36:42.360 --> 36:44.320
<font color="#00ffff">I don't believe you.</font>

36:44.320 --> 36:46.040
<font color="#00ffff">I'm going to tell Monsieur Marchal.</font>

36:46.040 --> 36:47.720
<font color="#ffff00">You will do what I tell you.</font>

36:49.360 --> 36:51.160
<font color="#00ffff">You don't scare me.</font>

36:51.160 --> 36:53.040
<font color="#ffff00">Maybe not, but Leopold does.</font>

36:57.640 --> 36:58.800
<font color="#00ffff">You work for my uncle?</font>

37:03.320 --> 37:05.800
<font color="#ffffff">Where is the King?</font>

37:05.800 --> 37:07.680
<font color="#ffffff">WHERE IS THE KING?</font>

37:07.680 --> 37:12.080
<font color="#ffffff">His hands are the claws</font>
<font color="#ffffff">of a craven beast.</font>

37:12.080 --> 37:15.240
<font color="#ffffff">His tongue is the snake of poison.</font>

37:15.240 --> 37:17.400
<font color="#ffffff">SHE SHRIEKS</font>

37:17.400 --> 37:19.360
<font color="#ffffff">HE SPEAKS LATIN</font>

37:19.360 --> 37:23.520
<font color="#ffffff">His hands are the claws</font>
<font color="#ffffff">of a craven beast!</font>

37:23.520 --> 37:26.720
<font color="#ffffff">His eyes are the pits of hell,</font>

37:26.720 --> 37:29.640
<font color="#ffffff">in which all mortals will perish</font>

37:29.640 --> 37:32.360
<font color="#ffffff">to tumble through purgatories!</font>

37:32.360 --> 37:35.000
<font color="#ffffff">For all eternity!</font>

37:35.000 --> 37:36.960
<font color="#ffffff">She is suffering terribly, sire.</font>

37:38.000 --> 37:39.840
<font color="#ffffff">You must go to her - she needs you.</font>

37:42.840 --> 37:43.880
<font color="#ffff00">What can I do for her?</font>

37:45.640 --> 37:47.080
<font color="#ffff00">Show her godliness.</font>

37:51.040 --> 37:53.000
<font color="#ffffff">What have you done to me?!</font>

37:53.000 --> 37:54.960
<font color="#ffffff">I beg you, let me go!</font>

37:54.960 --> 37:58.600
<font color="#ffffff">MAN SPEAKS LATIN</font>

37:58.600 --> 37:59.920
<font color="#ffffff">Begone!</font>

37:59.920 --> 38:01.480
<font color="#ffffff">You lied to me!</font>

38:01.480 --> 38:04.240
<font color="#ffffff">SHE SOBS</font>

38:04.240 --> 38:07.480
<font color="#ffffff">SOBBING: My flesh is on fire.</font>

38:07.480 --> 38:09.800
<font color="#ffffff">I beg you!</font>

38:09.800 --> 38:12.160
<font color="#ffffff">Give me peace!</font>

38:27.440 --> 38:28.480
<font color="#ffff00">Be still.</font>

38:32.440 --> 38:34.080
<font color="#ffff00">Peace be upon you.</font>

38:36.840 --> 38:38.800
<font color="#ffff00">Return to me.</font>

38:46.720 --> 38:48.480
<font color="#ffffff">Thank you.</font>

38:53.320 --> 38:57.960
<font color="#00ffff">The King...has cast out the demon.</font>

38:59.560 --> 39:01.560
<font color="#00ff00">It is a miracle.</font>

39:11.440 --> 39:14.360
<font color="#ffffff">The Queen remains gravely ill.</font>

39:14.360 --> 39:17.440
<font color="#ffffff">But her soul has been saved.</font>

39:17.440 --> 39:20.520
<font color="#ffffff">The King has performed a miracle.</font>

39:20.520 --> 39:23.280
<font color="#ffffff">APPLAUSE</font>

39:29.040 --> 39:31.360
<font color="#ffff00">Such wonderful news.</font>

39:31.360 --> 39:33.840
<font color="#ffff00">Word has it he saved her</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with his own hands.</font>

39:33.840 --> 39:35.840
<font color="#00ffff">I witnessed it myself.</font>

39:35.840 --> 39:39.280
<font color="#00ffff">Our Lord moves within him.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Excellent.</font>

39:39.280 --> 39:41.720
<font color="#ffff00">So perhaps now might be</font>
<font color="#ffff00">an apt moment</font>

39:41.720 --> 39:44.360
<font color="#ffff00">to approach him</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with a modest request?</font>

39:44.360 --> 39:49.280
<font color="#ffff00">You see, I was wondering about</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the Protestant arrangement.</font>

39:49.280 --> 39:51.880
<font color="#ffff00">We all agree it's a good idea,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">naturally.</font>

39:51.880 --> 39:56.880
<font color="#ffff00">However, I was hoping His Majesty</font>
<font color="#ffff00">might indulge certain individuals.</font>

39:56.880 --> 39:59.640
<font color="#ffff00">The Duchesse d'Angers, for example.</font>

39:59.640 --> 40:03.160
<font color="#ffff00">Her nephew's got a very bright</font>
<font color="#ffff00">future in stained glass.</font>

40:03.160 --> 40:04.320
<font color="#00ffff">Perhaps.</font>

40:05.400 --> 40:06.680
<font color="#00ffff">As a Catholic.</font>

40:11.400 --> 40:15.520
<font color="#ffff00">I was praying you might</font>
<font color="#ffff00">find it in your heart...</font>

40:15.520 --> 40:16.960
<font color="#ffff00">to help an old friend.</font>

40:21.760 --> 40:24.480
<font color="#00ffff">Incidentally, your services</font>

40:24.480 --> 40:26.920
<font color="#00ffff">as Master of Ceremony</font>
<font color="#00ffff">are no longer required.</font>

40:30.320 --> 40:33.640
<font color="#ffff00">But...the King appointed me.</font>

40:33.640 --> 40:36.320
<font color="#00ffff">The King has total faith</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in my judgment.</font>

42:05.040 --> 42:07.120
<font color="#ffffff">His Majesty should be pleased.</font>

42:07.120 --> 42:10.240
<font color="#ffffff">So many prominent Protestants</font>
<font color="#ffffff">have seen the light.</font>

42:19.000 --> 42:22.920
<font color="#ffff00">I bless you for your</font>
<font color="#ffff00">wisdom and humility...</font>

42:22.920 --> 42:25.480
<font color="#ffff00">and welcome you back</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to the one true Church.</font>

42:42.120 --> 42:44.360
<font color="#00ffff">Corpus Christi.</font>

42:46.760 --> 42:48.360
<font color="#00ffff">Corpus Christi.</font>

42:50.200 --> 42:51.760
<font color="#00ffff">Corpus Christi.</font>

42:56.440 --> 42:57.800
<font color="#00ffff">Corpus Christi.</font>

43:04.960 --> 43:06.800
<font color="#00ffff">Corpus Christi.</font>

43:46.520 --> 43:48.480
<font color="#ffffff">I know who you are.</font>

43:54.520 --> 43:55.960
<font color="#ffffff">Knight of Damascus.</font>

44:54.680 --> 44:58.360
<font color="#ffffff">Who is the man in the iron mask?</font>

44:58.360 --> 45:01.280
<font color="#ffff00">The King...</font>

45:01.280 --> 45:03.640
<font color="#ffff00">is not...</font>

45:03.640 --> 45:06.520
<font color="#ffff00">chosen by God.</font>

45:36.760 --> 45:38.600
<font color="#ffffff">WEAKLY: I can't see your face.</font>

45:42.920 --> 45:44.600
<font color="#ffffff">More candles.</font>

45:44.600 --> 45:46.440
<font color="#ffff00">It is daylight, my Queen.</font>

45:57.920 --> 45:59.840
<font color="#ffffff">So be it.</font>

46:10.920 --> 46:12.960
<font color="#ffffff">Will you be by my side?</font>

46:22.680 --> 46:24.160
<font color="#ffff00">I am with you.</font>

46:27.200 --> 46:28.760
<font color="#ffffff">I thought I would be afraid.</font>

46:31.840 --> 46:34.360
<font color="#ffffff">But not now, with</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the darkness approaching.</font>

46:36.080 --> 46:38.440
<font color="#ffffff">Perhaps because I know</font>
<font color="#ffffff">God will embrace me.</font>

46:41.320 --> 46:42.600
<font color="#ffff00">I admire your strength.</font>

46:45.560 --> 46:47.120
<font color="#ffff00">My faith has been tested often.</font>

46:48.760 --> 46:50.560
<font color="#ffff00">Yours is constant.</font>

46:50.560 --> 46:53.720
<font color="#ffff00">And I never made you happy.</font>

46:53.720 --> 46:56.960
<font color="#ffffff">Our life is not meant to be so.</font>

46:56.960 --> 46:59.760
<font color="#ffffff">That doesn't mean I don't love you.</font>

46:59.760 --> 47:01.480
<font color="#ffff00">You hold no regrets?</font>

47:04.640 --> 47:05.680
<font color="#ffffff">Just one.</font>

47:08.040 --> 47:11.160
<font color="#ffffff">I wish I could see the sunrise</font>
<font color="#ffffff">in Madrid once more.</font>

47:13.840 --> 47:16.600
<font color="#ffffff">To feel the warmth</font>
<font color="#ffffff">of home on my face.</font>

47:22.040 --> 47:24.280
<font color="#ffffff">Can you ever forgive me?</font>

47:31.440 --> 47:33.560
<font color="#ffff00">I should be asking that of you.</font>

47:33.560 --> 47:34.960
<font color="#ffffff">Of course I do.</font>

47:37.760 --> 47:39.600
<font color="#ffffff">We're all sinners.</font>

47:42.240 --> 47:45.400
<font color="#ffffff">We do not choose this life,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">we do our best within it.</font>

47:45.400 --> 47:47.320
<font color="#ffffff">You are a man like any other.</font>

47:52.680 --> 47:55.000
<font color="#ffffff">Do you recall when we first met?</font>

47:57.080 --> 47:58.240
<font color="#ffff00">Of course.</font>

48:01.800 --> 48:03.160
<font color="#ffffff">You smiled.</font>

48:06.120 --> 48:08.520
<font color="#ffffff">I was so frightened.</font>

48:09.960 --> 48:12.040
<font color="#ffffff">All those cold eyes staring.</font>

48:13.160 --> 48:18.560
<font color="#ffffff">My hands were shaking, I thought</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I would die, but you smiled.</font>

48:19.560 --> 48:23.640
<font color="#ffffff">Just a little.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">And I knew you were a good man.</font>

48:25.040 --> 48:28.080
<font color="#ffffff">You should smile more often,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">dear Louis.</font>

48:36.960 --> 48:38.640
<font color="#ffff00">How can I thank you?</font>

48:40.520 --> 48:42.680
<font color="#ffffff">Let's pray together as one.</font>

48:44.400 --> 48:46.440
<font color="#ffffff">Even for a moment.</font>

48:58.120 --> 48:59.840
<font color="#ffffff">SHE GASPS</font>

49:06.800 --> 49:09.360
<font color="#ffffff">Remember your heart.</font>

49:48.840 --> 49:50.520
<font color="#ffff00">I ask just one thing, Lord.</font>

49:53.040 --> 49:54.480
<font color="#ffff00">For my wife.</font>

49:57.200 --> 49:59.160
<font color="#ffff00">I beg you to give her peace.</font>

51:33.000 --> 51:34.840
<font color="#ffffff">Sire, the Queen...</font>

53:26.480 --> 53:28.080
<font color="#ffffff">HE GASPS</font>

